00:50:52,283 --> 00:50:58,966
or any other art to get inspired for Sea of Solitude. It came from the inside.

492
00:51:00,901 --> 00:51:05,562
art-wise, like the visual I drew from everything I learned, the visual like everything I learned

493
00:51:06,383 --> 00:51:15,666
so far and the style I have developed throughout my life so far. For the story I just let out what

