502
00:52:14,235 --> 00:52:20,159
So what I learned through the whole production of SOS,

503
00:52:21,600 --> 00:52:26,864
be it for the art, the story or every creative process,

504
00:52:27,584 --> 00:52:31,347
draw from what is inside you.

505
00:52:32,127 --> 00:52:35,710
Then it will have the biggest chance to be unique.

506
00:52:36,510 --> 00:52:39,592
Adore other's art, but be careful

507
00:52:39,612 --> 00:52:42,615
to not adapt it accidentally.

508
00:52:44,161 --> 00:52:51,104
I stopped looking at others art too much at some point and I think this is why

509
00:52:51,124 --> 00:52:59,667
the Solitude became a bit more unique. From now on I will always follow the path of first

510
00:52:59,787 --> 00:53:06,469
looking inside me, take the strongest emotion or thought I have at the point in my life

511
00:53:06,889 --> 00:53:12,811
and use that as a base for the art or the games I want to create.

512
00:53:13,827 --> 00:53:22,249
This way it will likely have the personality, have personality and will be unique.

513
00:53:22,889 --> 00:53:32,712
And I think that is the key we all, all the artists out there, want to achieve. Thank you.

